<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>{{ article.titre }}</title>
    <style>
        @page {
            margin: 0;
        }

        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: #f9fafb;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 50px 60px;
        }

        .header {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .logo {
            width: 60px;
            height: 60px;
        }

        .site-title {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #c084fc;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #c084fc;
            font-size: 28px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .info-block {
            background-color: #111827;
            border-left: 4px solid #c084fc;
            padding: 15px 20px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }

        .label {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #a1a1aa;
        }

        .divider {
            border-top: 1px solid #374151;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 14px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }

        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #9ca3af;
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 60px;
        }

        .footer strong {
            color: #facc15;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="header">
        <div class="site-title">Le meilleur blog musique de sa génération</div>
        {% if logoBase64 %}
            <img src="{{ logoBase64 }}" alt="Logo" style="width: 80px; height: auto; margin-top: 10px;">
        {% endif %}
    </div>

    <h1>{{ article.titre }}</h1>

    <p>{{ article.contenu|nl2br }}</p>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="info-block">
        <p><span class="label">Artiste :</span> {{ article.artiste }}</p>
        <p><span class="label">Date de publication :</span> {{ article.datePublication|date('d/m/Y') }}</p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <div class="footer">
        Ce document a été généré automatiquement dans le cadre du projet scolaire Symfony - Music Blog.<br>
        Oui c'est pas ouf comme template de pdf.
    </div>

</body>
</html>